        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <i class="feature-icon fas fa-truck"></i>
            <h3>Fast Shipping</h3>
            <p>Enjoy quick and reliable shipping to your doorstep. Plant your seeds without delay!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <i class="feature-icon fas fa-dollar-sign"></i>
            <h3>Competitive Prices</h3>
